/a>  and <a href=\"/best-people-search-services\"><u>people searches</u></a>  use information from these sources, though you would have to search multiple databases to get the information provided in one people search report."]},"id":"a31ff27d-8db6-4398-8d50-035679f072ea","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Depending on which state you live in, public records can extend even further. Some states make public record of unemployment claims, campaign contributions, licenses and certifications, tax information, real estate transactions and deeds, census records and more.","This means that people can find out everything from your phone number to your bankruptcy records to what kind of boat you own. Many online companies use public records databases to run background check  and people search  services. It is a good idea to find out what kinds of public records are available where you live. There are many state government websites that have links to that information; you can also try www.publicrecordfinder.com to find out specifics of state public records laws.","You can also find out more about the services that use public records in our reviews of  and background check services people search services. These services use public records to give you a report about someone much faster and easier than if you had done all the research yourself. Take a look at our side-by-side comparison  to see which services ranked best in our review."]},"id":"624d120a-305b-4c71-8c6e-13a3c6a2bc9c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_699","url":"/what-are-public-records","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"dan-hope","url":"/author/dan-hope","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Dan Hope","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"ciX3esGRJxxonvFVhNC6p6","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","datePublished":"2014-11-06T21:54:38Z","name":"What are Public Records?","synopsis":"You might be 